result.text:
UN Chief Guterres on Israel/Hamas war: at crucial moment like this vital to be clear on principles, starting with protection of civilians. 

Guterres says Hamas attacks 'did not happen in vacuum', Palestinians have been subjected to 56 years of 'suffocating occupation'. 

Guterres says Palestinian grievances cannot justify appalling Hamas attacks, and those attacks cannot justify collective Palestinian punishment.

Guterres says deeply concerned about clear violations of international humanitarian law that we are witnessing in Gaza and  insist on a ceasefire in the Middle East. #CGTNUN
